Name: Flappy Fish Toy
Description:
Treat Your Ferret to Endless Fun with Our Electric Funny Cat Simulation Fish Toy!

Give your ferret the gift of excitement and entertainment with our Electric Funny Cat Simulation Fish Toy, designed to provide hours of amusement for your furry friend. As a ferret owner, you know how important it is to keep your pet mentally stimulated and engaged, and this innovative toy delivers just that.

Weighing only 100g, this lightweight toy is the perfect addition to your ferret's collection of throwing toys. Equipped with a built-in touch sensor, the toy automatically activates when your ferret interacts with it, swinging and making enticing sounds to captivate your pet's attention.

But that's not all – our wiggle fish toy features a USB rechargeable design, eliminating the need for batteries and saving you both time and money. Plus, the detachable motor makes cleaning a breeze, ensuring that your ferret's toy stays fresh and hygienic for endless play sessions.

Crafted from high-quality PP cotton, this realistic flopping fish toy is safe and non-toxic for your ferret to play with, providing peace of mind for you as a pet owner. Measuring 30cm in size, it's the perfect size for your ferret to pounce on and wrestle with to their heart's content.

Give your ferret the gift of excitement and enrichment with our Electric Funny Cat Simulation Fish Toy. Because every moment of play is a moment of joy for your beloved pet!
